SAYLOR
I mean, don't you know?  There's an app.  You type a name and it sounds every time you enter the doors of some store that supports this app.  Look.

SAYLOR leaves the store and enters again.

ROBOTIC VOICE
Welcome again, Saylor!  Your second visit today.

SAYLOR
Ah, seems like the app is updated.  Earlier it didn't say the number of visits.  Anyways.

